videos.headline: Ayers makes diving catch on second try
videos.description: Houston's Greg Ward's pass is almost intercepted, then goes off Demarcus Ayers' should pads to pop in the air before Ayers makes the diving catch to complete the unorthodox 23 yard gain. Houston would score on the drive to go up 14-7.

videos.headline: Ward's miraculous escape results in Houston TD
videos.description: Houston's Greg Ward Jr. looks trapped inside the pocket but the Cougars quarterback puts on a sweet spin move, gets free and finds the end zone to put Houston up 21-14.

videos.description: Houston's Demarcus Ayers makes a dazzling one-handed catch over the middle and then finds open field to race into the end zone, extending the Cougars' lead to 38-17.
